Lore: The Key Master commissioned this bronze to a talented
bronzesmith. Most villagers speculate on the identity of the
mysterious head. But one tale resonates the most;
Lord Hoskinson came from far and brought wealth to the
village. Thus, the Key Master wanted to pay
homage to his philanthropy.
